    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute favorite ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, so you can count on it being ready for all your weekend trips or the daily commute! Everything runs smoothly, and it still looks great parked in the driveway. I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it just as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
