      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65B40 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a cross-plane crank to deliver linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, the chassis dynamics remain sharp and predictable. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the structural integrity of the rotating assembly. The EDC (Electronic Damper Control) system provides versatile damping profiles, while the subframe bushings remain firm. A driver-focused example that balances track-capable kinematics with daily usability.",
      "price": 36500.0,
